<div class="postcell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
                
<p>I want to do something like class categories in Objective-C, to define a class in one file, implement some core methods there, then implement some helper methods in another without subclassing or interfaces, just "continue" the class.</p>

<p>Possible in PHP?</p>
    </div>

