            <div class="comment-body js-comment-edit-hide">
                
                <span class="comment-copy">Semantic stuff. A class managing the database is not really like a children of some class with helper methods only. Anyway, I will compose the tools via a simple instance then.</span>
                
                <div class="d-inline-flex ai-center">
